      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Niels Abildskov</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"/File:NielsAbildskov.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/NielsAbildskov.jpg/240px-NielsAbildskov.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/NielsAbildskov.jpg/360px-NielsAbildskov.jpg 1.5x, /images/d/da/NielsAbildskov.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:NielsAbildskov.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Niels Abildskov <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Niels Abildskov</b>,<br />\na Danish computer scientits with interests in computer chess programming. \nHe is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engines</a> <i>Copper</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/Loki\" title=\"Loki\">Loki</a>.\nCopper, his first chess engine trial was heavily influenced by <a href=\"/Vice\" title=\"Vice\">Vice</a>, is actually buggy and superseded by Loki <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niels_Abildskov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76483\">Transposition table and multithreaded search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Shared_Hash_Table\" title=\"Shared Hash Table\">Shared Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76491\">Sorting moves during move ordering</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 04, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76499\">Transposition table replacement scheme</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#ReplacementStrategies\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Replacement Strategies</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76521\">Endgame recognition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 07, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76529\">Effective branching factor question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 08, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Branching_Factor#EBF\" title=\"Branching Factor\">Effective Branching Factor</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76835\">Staged move generation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 10, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation#Staged\" title=\"Move Generation\">Staged Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76976\">King safety evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 29, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77105\">Progress on Loki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77118\">Tuning search parameters</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 18, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77152\">Move ordering heuristics for captures</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 23, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77189\">Listening for GUI input when searching</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a>, <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77420\">A hybrid of SPSA and local optimization</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/SPSA\" title=\"SPSA\">SPSA</a>, <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77105&amp;start=74\">Staged move generation done right (Progress on Loki)</a>] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niels_Abildskov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/BimmerBass\">BimmerBass (Niels Abildskov) · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Niels_Abildskov&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/BimmerBass\">BimmerBass (Niels Abildskov) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/BimmerBass/CopperChess\">GitHub - BimmerBass/CopperChess</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77105\">Progress on Loki</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Niels Abildskov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2021</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228124354\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7806-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228124354 and revision id 25662\n -->\n"
